rows.label: qst711601_msg0001
rows.name:
Mo! That guy, I can't forgive
him, mo! Punpun is mad, mo!

rows.label: qst711601_msg0004
rows.name:
When Punpun was napping
in my favorite spot, it
suddenly attacked me, mo!

rows.label: qst711601_msg0005
rows.name:
At this rate, it's revenge,
mo! Vengeance, mo!

rows.label: qst711601_msg0006
rows.name:
But Punpun is an adventurer
who loves peace and naps,
so I can't fight, mo.

rows.label: qst711601_msg0007
rows.name:
I just want to see that guy's
troubled face a little, mo.

rows.label: qst711601_msg0008
rows.name: That's where you all come in, mo!

rows.label: qst711601_msg0009
rows.name:
On Punpun's behalf, please
punish that guy's comrades, mo!

rows.label: qst711601_msg0010
rows.name:
Even monsters should reflect
a little when their comrades
are beaten, mo!

rows.label: qst711601_msg0011
rows.name:
By the way, that guy's name
is Myrrhes Crustip, mo!

rows.label: qst711601_msg0012
rows.name:
...The fact that he sounds stronger
than Punpun is annoying, mo.

rows.label: qst711601_msg0013
rows.name:
Anyway, that guy's comrades are all
over the swamp near this camp, mo!

rows.label: qst711601_msg0014
rows.name:
If you defeat about three of them,
Punpun will be satisfied, mo!

rows.label: qst711601_msg0015
rows.name:
Well then, Punpun will wait
here with safety first, mo!
